title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: Ruslaan
subTitle: A terrorist's son tries to fix his reputation after an anti-terrorism officer adopts him.

title: House No. 13
subTitle: Movie starring Arjun and Gayatri.

title: Satya Gang
subTitle: Satya and Raj, who are orphans, own a garage and make a living out of it. However, their lives turn tragic when a notorious gang commit numerous murders and make them the culprits.

title: Yajamana
subTitle: Krishna, the son-in-law of the village head, tries to defend his village by fighting against a cruel criminal disguised as a business tycoon, Devi Shetty.

title: Haunted Mahal
subTitle: When mysterious deaths plague a haunted bungalow, a young man begins to investigate. However, his research leads him to uncover the mansion's dark past and ghostly secrets.

title: Hidimbha
subTitle: In Hyderabad, two police officers begin to investigate a case, but more people go missing in the process. All the victims are girls, with one other interesting commonality.

title: Bogan
subTitle: A police officer who is working on a bank robbery case arrests a man who is harbouring a supernatural secret.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: Varun, an NRI medical student, and Bhanu, a vivacious young woman, fall in love with each other. However, they face many personal differences, creating complications in their relationship.

title: Sultan
subTitle: A middle-aged wrestling champion tries to make a comeback to represent India at the Olympics.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Yuvaraj
subTitle: Yuva enrols in an engineering college after getting banned from his sport and picks up fights with local students. However, his life gets more strained when his father flees, owing a huge debt.

title: The Great Indian Butterfly
subTitle: A young couple named Krish and Meera are confused and frustrated at the corporate rat race unfolding around them and, as an antidote, they they go in search of a legendary magical insect.

title: Son Of Devil
subTitle: After Karan saves Sonu from a group of thugs, the latter falls in love with him.

title: Deewar Man of Power
subTitle: Bujji and Chitti are good childhood friends, but after a fall-out Chitti asks Bujji not to see her again for 12 years, however, she promises to marry him after this time. Bujji then goes to live in Chennai and becomes a 'goonda'.

title: Spy
subTitle: An agent unravels the connection between a notorious arms dealer and the hidden secrets of Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose, risking everything to protect India from impending chaos.

title: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
subTitle: When a lawyer uncovers a ruthless leader's criminal network that sexually exploits and threatens young women, he embarks on a bloody pursuit of justice.

title: Mardaani 2
subTitle: Shivani Shivaji Roy locks horns with the devil incarnate, a young and remorseless serial killer who is raping and murdering young women.

title: Gatta Kusthi
subTitle: When wrestling champ Keerthi enters an arranged marriage with a chauvinistic Veera, she scrambles to be a traditional wife while hiding her true self.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Disillusioned with his exams, an aspiring police candidate traces the footsteps of Alluri, a passionate officer who stopped at nothing to fulfil his duties and combat all types of corruption.

title: Mission 118
subTitle: An investigative journalist has nightmares about a young woman's murder and tries to uncover whether his dreams have any connection to reality.

title: Mission 118
subTitle: An investigative journalist has nightmares about a young woman's murder and tries to uncover whether his dreams have any connection to reality.

title: Pankh
subTitle: Film highlighting a phenomenon peculiar and exclusive to the Indian film industry, the practise of casting children in roles opposite to their natural genders.

title: 1947: Earth
subTitle: The disaster of Indian/Pakistani partition seen through the eyes of a child - Lenny, an eight-year-old crippled girl - from Lahore, the Punjabi city that saw some of the bloodiest pogroms. The experiences, hopes and fears of this young girl provide an intense portrait of the period.

title: Rowdy Baadshah
subTitle: Sadhu Bhai is a notorious mafia leader who escaped India after various terrorist attacks and conquered the entire Southeast Asia. No one dares to challenge Sadhu Bhai. Baadshah enters the underworld for his father. In the opening scene, Sadhu Bhai's partner, Crazy Robert, captures Baadshah and his father as Baadshah revolts against Sadhu Bhai. But Baadshah easily defeats Crazy Robert's goons. Baadshah tries to find a solution as the Indian police and Hong Kong police are looking for him.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three teens come to Bangalore for their engineering education and get involved in a fight. They find a local gangster to help them.

title: Maragadha Naanayam
subTitle: Two small-time thieves who work for a jewel smuggler take up a contract to locate a cursed emerald medallion. With the help of a priest, they summon three spirits to guide them in their quest.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a devoted architect from Hyderabad, juggles supporting his extended family while seeking a partner who understands his commitments. When he discovers Aadhya's thesis on his family, he challenges her, leading to unexpected twists.

title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
subTitle: The story revolves around a family's hidden secrets; a daughter's craving for her mother's affection and her mother's constant rejection of her. Watch the drama unfold.

title: Maargan
subTitle: A serial killer targets women with a strange serum that turns their bodies black. Subsequently, a high-ranking police officer sets out to catch the culprit.

title: Liger -- Saala Crossbreed
subTitle: A bravehearted Liger works his way up to find his dream spot in the MMA world, but his life gets complicated when he crosses paths with Taniya.
